BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString: tell application "OmniFocus"	tell the default document to tell the front document window				set perspective name to "Due Soon"		set theTasks to tree of content		set taskNames to {}				repeat with a from 1 to length of theTasks			set theTask to the value of (item a of theTasks)			set myTask to get name of theTask			set myDate to get due date of theTask			set myTags to get tags of theTask			set myWeekday to "No Due Date"			if (myDate is not missing value) then set myWeekday to weekday of myDate						set end of taskNames to (myTask & " (" & myWeekday & ") , ")					end repeat				return characters 1 thru ((length of (taskNames as string)) - 2) of (taskNames as string) as string			end tellend tell
